濟主義理念不同，c生擔心香港左傾係犯左邏輯根本性既錯誤。"},{"pid":"8d9c65dd21dceaaee4ea23919e041d85afe68332","tid":1886385,"uid":28121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母香港依家搞成咁<br />\n都剩係識講錢錢錢"},{"pid":"3eef21c5ed275ff18a0e07d98700d2aebe86d4c7","tid":1886385,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"藍絲真係好奇怪嘅生物，自己話愛國但居然對社會主義反感，真係身體好誠實！"},{"pid":"987bbf3bd2518a0e871434b458703f6169a81e5b","tid":1886385,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6c18d1c494c050d640835957be1f35a897c331","tid":1886385,"uid":102700,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"47f31fdddf680903a934fa9afe97b6e0565ddc96","tid":1886385,"uid":228955,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣梗係唔想啦如果郁啲都封關開咗個先例 點叫人上去大灣區買樓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:11:26.000Z","msg":"大陸都唔侵中原玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"唔玩都好點都要分一杯羹"},{"pid":"a8573b30eafcfa3040692b019966d325c5f300f9","tid":1886385,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"廢老返去讀下歷史啦"},{"pid":"8b596f4dc330c202182a1e6619cb206dca17621b","tid":1886385,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"封關好似唔關資本主義社會主義事喎<br />\n格硬黎嘅喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d98cd445a61625c61f1041d311e42014424900c","tid":1886385,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣唔係好想2047一國一制咩？"},{"pid":"5c04606adf4cd82cfc76ff1ad4abadb8afbf25a7","tid":1886385,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"屍生好驚無得炒樓"},{"pid":"55e347770a97e8100cb7f880ffc840825bc519ed","tid":1886385,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply